com.microsoft.azure.management.network

Interface NetworkSecurityGroupOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NetworkSecurityGroupOperationsImpl

    public interface NetworkSecurityGroupOperations
    The Network Resource Provider API includes operations for managing the NetworkSecurityGroups for your subscription.
